#based on:
#https://github.com/php-fig/fig-standards/blob/master/accepted/PSR-0.md

#fully qualified namespace based folder structure
\<VendorName>\<Namespace>\<ClassName>
Toplevel namespace is <VendorName>
Each namespace separator is converted into a DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR
Each "_" in a classname is converted into a DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR
Each classname is extended with .php (likewise) as filename
Names in namespace, classname and vendorname can combine any lower and uppercase alphabetic characters
